title: "Who Is That Funny For" LIVE from Moontower Comedy Fest (w/ Chris Redd & guest host Joel Kim Booster)

description:
Bowen is joined by guest host Joel Kim Booster and guest Chris Redd live from the Moontower Comedy Fest in Austin. They discuss who it's funny for, the success of Joel's parents home censorship, Bowen's discovery of the problematic history of Kewpie dolls, and Adderall just being meth.
